Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: This package is intended to provide functions that are useful to
    run portfolio optimalizations with different objectives. The user provides
    security data and gets portfolios that are optimal with respect to different
    parameters. Included optimizations are equity and debt flexibly weigthed,
    Sharpe-Ratio optimized and Risk-parity. The portfolio will be constructed in
    accordance to the provided risk preference of the user
